_sText:
AWP Waterwall (granade) is a little, simple, strategic map.
Your weapons are: the normal pistols, or you can take the AWPs or granades, lying around.
You hav 2 ways, to kill the enemy.
1) Swimm to the big wall in the middle, and clib up.
2) Swimm to the big wall in the middle, and dive under it.. 
You can snipe then enemys from underwater, if they are in water.. or wait, until the enemys climb up the wall and shoot them xD

Have Fun!
